        <td><span class="badge b-half">HALF</span></td>
        <td>not Sep</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- MORNING FLOW + ENTRY MODEL -->
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px">

    <div class="sec blue">
      <div class="sec-title">Morning Flow — Every Day</div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">1</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>Pre-market:</strong> Mark PDH, PDL, London High, London Low on chart</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">2</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>8:00 AM:</strong> Did London close above PDH or below PDL? → T3/T4 fires</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">3</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>9:29 AM:</strong> Where is price? Above PDH = 52.9% bull disp. Below PDL = 49.4% bear disp.</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">4</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>11:00 AM:</strong> Check KZ close → T1/T2/T5/T6/T7/T8. No signal = no trade</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">5</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>3:00 PM:</strong> Close entry window. Continuation drops to 54%</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="sec">
      <div class="sec-title">3-Step Entry Model (all tiers)</div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">①</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>Liquidity sweep</strong> — price grabs SSL/BSL before reversing</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">②</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>CISD</strong> — engulfing candle closes back through opposing FVG</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">③</div><div class="rule-txt"><strong>OB retest</strong> — enter on pullback to Order Block. Stop below/above OB low/high</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="sec amber">
      <div class="sec-title">T3/T4 Entry Timing</div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">—</div><div class="rule-txt">T3/T4 fires at 8am → <strong>enter 9:30–2:30 PM</strong> on any pullback to key level</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">—</div><div class="rule-txt">T1/T2/T5/T6/T7/T8 → <strong>enter after 11am</strong> on first pullback post-KZ close</div></div>
      <div class="rule"><div class="rule-num">—</div><div class="rule-txt">T3+T1 fire same day = <strong>double confirmation</strong> — strongest bull day in model</div></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- ROW 2: PULLBACK DATA + SCORING + OVERNIGHT -->
<div class="grid">

